# 5 Things
Infrequent Daily Dose of things learned

# Reluctant Maven
My Personal opinions on topics I feel about and feel competent enough to express my opinions about. Usually not technology.

# Projects
My Projects, some academic some random, some biological, some sociological but predominantly technical. 

# About
A Proper chubby [Huduga ](http://www.shabdkosh.com/kn/translate/%E0%B2%B9%E0%B3%81%E0%B2%A1%E0%B3%81%E0%B2%97/%E0%B2%B9%E0%B3%81%E0%B2%A1%E0%B3%81%E0%B2%97-meaning-in-English-Kannada) from _Namma Bengaluru_. 
Computer Science, Mathematics, Biology, Football, Basketball, Test Cricket, Comics and Food, just loads of food are some things that keep me busy.
